com.xith3d.utility.interpolate
Class AngleInterpolater

java.lang.Object
  com.xith3d.utility.interpolate.AngleInterpolater
public class AngleInterpolater
extends Object

Creates a time based interpolator for angles. The result is an angle in radians appropriate to use as a euler angle. The speed is specfied in radians/second. The interpolator can be increasing or decreasing. Copyright: Copyright (c) 2000,2001 Company: Teseract Software, LLP

Author:
David Yazel
